---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Markdown from '../components/Markdown.astro';

const explainer = `
**AmicBridge connects people to exclusive private opportunities — safely and directly.**

We don’t hold money or approve transactions.  
We simply help people discover each other, talk privately, and make their own agreements.

### How It Works
1. Create a profile.  
2. Browse opportunities or describe what you’re looking for.  
3. Connect privately with the right people.

All financial decisions happen *outside* our platform — we are the bridge, not the middleman.

### What You Can Do Here
– Access exclusive private opportunities.  
– Connect directly with private lenders, borrowers, or investors.  
– Communicate securely and privately.  
– Build trust with verified profiles.  
– Stay safe with clear guidelines.

AmicBridge is about **connection**, not control.  
You stay in charge — we simply help you meet the right people.
`;
---

<Layout title="Welcome to AmicBridge">

  <!-- Main Title -->
  <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8">Welcome to AmicBridge</h1>

  <!-- Main Text -->
  <Markdown content={explainer} class="mb-12 text-lg leading-relaxed" />

  <!-- Create Profile Button -->
  <a 
    href="https://wa.me/4792928373?text=Hi%2C+I+want+to+create+a+profile+on+AmicBridge"
    target="_blank"
    class="bg-blue-400 hover:bg-blue-500 text-slate-900 font-semibold px-10 py-3 rounded-lg block text-center shadow-lg mb-10 w-max"
  >
    Create My Profile
  </a>

  <!-- Action Buttons -->
  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 mt-10">

    <!-- Loan Button -->
    <a 
      href="https://wa.me/4792928373?text=Hi%2C+I+need+a+loan+through+AmicBridge"
      target="_blank"
      class="bg-rose-400 hover:bg-rose-500 text-slate-900 font-semibold px-12 py-4 rounded-lg block text-center shadow-lg"
    >
      I Need a Loan
    </a>

    <!-- Lend / Invest Button -->
    <a 
      href="https://wa.me/4792928373?text=Hi%2C+I+want+to+offer+capital+through+AmicBridge"
      target="_blank"
      class="bg-rose-400 hover:bg-rose-500 text-slate-900 font-semibold px-12 py-4 rounded-lg block text-center shadow-lg"
    >
      I Want to Lend / Invest
    </a>

  </div>

  <!-- Pricing & Unlock Info -->
  <section class="mt-16 max-w-2xl space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Payment for unlocking contact</h2>

    <p class="text-slate-300">
      AmicBridge does not take part in your agreements or charge any fee on the money you move.
      Instead, we charge a small fee when you want to unlock the direct contact details of a
      person or opportunity that matches you.
    </p>

    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-300 space-y-1">
      <li>You first contact us on WhatsApp and tell us what you are looking for.</li>
      <li>We search our network for a suitable match.</li>
      <li>When you want their direct contact details, you pay a one-time unlock fee.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="text-slate-300">
      Current unlock fee: <strong>499 NOK per contact</strong>.
    </p>

    <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">
      Payment is handled directly with AmicBridge (for example via Vipps to <strong>92928373</strong>).
      After payment is confirmed, we send you the contact details of the matching person or opportunity.
      All agreements and money transfers still happen privately between you and the other party — 
      AmicBridge never holds or manages client funds.
    </p>
  </section>

</Layout>
